{"tid":885111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港豬支那居住證】7萬港豬申請，支蛆黃柳權：接受程度不高","createTime":"2018-11-01T06:07:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T10:28:57.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"445d7de926526a780c4801726b54b0a2b8c85e8f","tid":885111,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:07:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181031/58859121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181031%2F58859121&d=Vbv4rkH7z4CsAGwskV%2FJMMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=7fa54769\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181031%2F58859121&h=291e3d68\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181031/58859121</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181031/large/1540982372_72e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181031%2Flarge%2F1540982372_72e6.jpg&h=6d5eab96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港澳辦副主任黃柳權接受《紫荊》雜誌專訪時表示，自上月起實施港澳台居民居住證制度，截至上周六（27日），已近有超過8.2萬港澳居民申請，當中有近7萬是香港人。不過，黃柳權承認，居住證仍存在使用範圍不廣、接受程度不高的問題，內地一些公共服務和商業機構的機器無法辨識居住證，相信仍需一些時間提升相關軟硬件。 <br />\n<br />\n黃柳權又重申，居住證與稅收規定並無對應關係，稅務部門不會以是否領取居住證作為要在內地納稅的依據。內地在實施新個人所得稅法時，會考慮繼續對境外人士，包括港澳台人士作出有關優惠安排。另外，中央有關部門會進一步研究，能否擴大回鄉證在內地的應用範圍。"},{"pid":"ddbd7b6fc34361ba2507b076461f46b94380610d","tid":885111,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:15:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0497705e0e2b751e509512e938480a181b42f362","tid":885111,"uid":40628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:16:01.000Z","msg":"有幾多成係新移民同共諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa64817713e74480c9d6d6f952d8ac1968a1897","tid":885111,"uid":171192,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:19:41.000Z","msg":"香港740萬人<br />\n得7萬人申請<br />\n即係733萬人唔支持<br />\n反了反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62fd27580143a8864fac8bdef51334f1c380ae61","tid":885111,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:31:56.000Z","msg":"原來香港起碼有7萬港奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ac6c08458fa211a162937f7c99c0c9f1984244","tid":885111,"uid":145277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:41:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來香港起碼有7萬港奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實唔算多，你諗下150計劃同埋投資移民計劃（曾蔭權時期），都遠多於呢個數，多數申請居住證既都係伯伯婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ff2c33e3c61c72941ec962c017d6134423698b","tid":885111,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:28:57.000Z","msg":"港澳台？"}]}